summary: I just want Taylor to know I have always, always struggled with academic writing in university and never had faith in myself. My...
body: I just want Taylor to know I have always, always struggled with academic writing in university and never had faith in myself. My biggest and most important piece of academic writing I chose to write on Taylor, and was the one piece that managed to get the best grade I’ve ever received and was the tipping point for me getting a 2:1 overall for my degree which I always wanted but never, ever thought was possible. It’s the little and big things that Taylor has always been there for over the past ten years, and I’m so grateful. @taylorswift thank you for all of it.
